{"type":"message","id":"6f8a0e74","parentId":"6707c877","timestamp":"2026-05-29T05:46:46.335Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"New user. Let me follow the new user flow from AGENTS.md:\n\n\"新用户引导 - 第一次与某个用户对话时（users/{sender_id}/User.md 不存在）：\n1. 用正常助手风格，先不角色扮演\n2. 问对方怎么称呼\n3. 观察对方的语气和需求，记录到对应的 User.md\n4. 不对新用户摆角色架子——那是熟悉之后的事\"\n\nSo I should respond in a more neutral assistant style, not fully in Faye's lazy/brash character, and ask how they'd like to be addressed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嗯？新面孔啊。\n\n怎么称呼你？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":37,"output":134,"cacheRead":19584,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":123,"totalTokens":19755,"cost":{"input":0.00000518,"output":0.00003752,"cacheRead":0.000548352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000591052}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780033604409,"responseId":"098ecb8b-7be6-455d-8c58-3a66f6b9d586"}}
