{"type":"message","id":"17b4f9b3","parentId":"0808acfa","timestamp":"2026-05-29T05:51:01.268Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user asked for \"/菜单\" (menu). According to AGENTS.md:\n\n```\n\"/菜单\" → spawn Spirit 返回 bot_function_explain.md\n```\n\nWait, let me re-read more carefully:\n\n```\n命中 trigger_prompt.md？\n  │\n  ├─ YES ─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  │   ├─ \"/菜单\"    → spawn Spirit 返回 bot_function_explain.md\n```\n\nActually, let me check the trigger_prompt.md to see what it says about menus. But actually the AGENTS.md says /菜单 should spawn Spirit to return bot_function_explain.md.\n\nLet me spawn Spirit for this task.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Kus9dbRj5gI8GJ9fSgGt6523","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"spirit","task":"一位新用户（还没告诉我名字）想看功能列表。去读 bot_function_explain.md，把已注册功能整理成一份用户友好的菜单返回给我。","mode":"run"},"partialArgs":"{\"agentId\": \"spirit\", \"task\": \"一位新用户（还没告诉我名字）想看功能列表。去读 bot_function_explain.md，把已注册功能整理成一份用户友好的菜单返回给我。\", \"mode\": \"run\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":16501,"output":241,"cacheRead":3456,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":130,"totalTokens":20198,"cost":{"input":0.00231014,"output":0.00006748000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00009676799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002474388}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780033857717,"responseId":"8dc847fb-536c-4f3e-a0db-385f5c5dfda8"}}
