{"type":"message","id":"c1bc3430","parentId":"4f9ad054","timestamp":"2026-05-29T05:51:17.925Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Spirit has returned the function list. Let me forward this to the user. The user hasn't told me their name yet, but they asked for the menu, so I'll deliver it.\n\nPer AGENTS.md: \"直接转发 Son 的返回文本给用户，不加戏不改内容\" — but this is from Spirit, not Son. Still, the principle applies — forward the menu info.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"喏，目前船上装的东西：\n\n---\n\n**1. 🧊 漂流瓶**\n匿名扔消息到公共瓶海，捞别人的瓶，回别人的瓶\n- `/扔瓶子` — 扔一条\n- `/捞瓶子` — 捞一条\n- `/看瓶子` — 翻自己扔过的\n- `/回复瓶子` — 回复捞到的\n\n**2. 📝 备忘录**\n记待办、改状态、删备忘\n- `/记备忘录` — 记一条\n- `/看备忘录` — 全览\n- `/改备忘录` — 改内容\n- `/修改状态` — 完成/进行中\n- `/删备忘录` — 删除\n\n**3. ⛅ 早朝官**\n每天早上8点自动推：待办 + 漂流瓶摘要 + 小故事啥的\n- `/早朝` — 立马看\n- `/设早朝 HH:MM` — 改推送时间\n- `/关早朝` — 关了清净\n\n**4. 🖼️ 相册笔记**\n存照片带注释，回头能搜\n- `/存照片` — 存\n- `/看相册` — 翻\n- `/搜照片` — 搜\n- `/删照片` — 删\n\n---\n\n有想试的直接喊。另外——你还没告诉我怎么称呼你呢 😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":17371,"output":371,"cacheRead":3584,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":81,"totalTokens":21326,"cost":{"input":0.00243194,"output":0.00010388,"cacheRead":0.000100352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0026361720000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780033873684,"responseId":"ee64d43c-f7e8-4c2c-9793-2e2c704a3db1"}}
